&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style=3D'line-height:115%'>The illustrations in (b) abo=
ve
merely state the principle involved. The actual computation should be made =
by
use of the coefficient table as appropriate. (See “Transcription and
Computation Short Cuts for Overtime”.)</span></p>

