<h4><b>32g08&nbsp; Sec 7(f) plans and the PCA.</b></h4>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'line-height:115%'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'margin-left:.25in'><span style=3D'line-height=
:115%'>A
Sec 7(f) plan which is found to be valid may continue to operate during per=
iods
in which the work of the employee is subject to the provisions of the PCA,
