p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'line-height:115%'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in'><span
style=3D'line-height:115%'>(2)<span style=3D'font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>=
&nbsp; </span></span><span
style=3D'line-height:115%'>an employee performing two or more kinds of work=
 for
which different hourly or piece rate, have been established, provided</span=
></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'line-height:115%'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal style=3D'margin-left:.75in;text-indent:-.25in'><span
